---

<Layout title="人工智能遊戲編程課程">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
  
  <HeroSection 
    title={courseData.title}
    subtitle={courseData.subtitle}
    tags={courseData.tags}
    heroImage={courseData.heroImage}
    description={courseData.description}
  />

  <!-- Hero image and description section -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <Image 
              src={aiGeneratedCodeImage} 
              alt="AI 編程新時代" 
              width={600}
              height={400}
              class="w-full h-auto"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">為什麼選擇 AI 編程？</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            在人工智能快速發展的時代，學會與 AI 協作進行網頁遊戲開發是未來的重要技能。本課程讓學生體驗 AI 輔助開發的樂趣，同時建立紮實的網頁編程思維。網頁遊戲開發相比其他平台更簡單，學生可以快速看到成果並分享給朋友。
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-cyan-500 mt-1"></i>
              <span class="text-gray-700">降低編程門檻，專注創意實現</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-cyan-500 mt-1"></i>
              <span class="text-gray-700">學習未來工作模式</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-cyan-500 mt-1"></i>
              <span class="text-gray-700">快速原型開發能力</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why the technology is important section -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">為什麼選用這些技術？</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <i class="fas fa-brain text-3xl text-cyan-500 mr-4"></i>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Poe 平台</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Poe 提供強大的 AI 助手，能幫助學生設計遊戲邏輯、生成代碼片段，讓編程過程更加直觀和高效。
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <i class="fas fa-cloud text-3xl text-cyan-500 mr-4"></i>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Repl.it 環境</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Repl.it 提供完整的雲端開發環境，無需本地安裝，支持多種編程語言，讓學生專注於創意實現。
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <i class="fas fa-gamepad text-3xl text-cyan-500 mr-4"></i>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">網頁遊戲開發</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            網頁遊戲相比其他平台遊戲更容易開發，無需複雜的安裝程序，學生可以快速看到成果並分享給朋友。通過遊戲開發學習編程，讓抽象的編程概念變得具體有趣。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Course requirements section -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">課程要求</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        {courseRequirements.map((requirement) => (
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow text-center">
            <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
              <i class={`${requirement.icon} text-3xl text-cyan-500`}></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">{requirement.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">{requirement.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Course highlights section -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">課程重點</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {courseHighlights.map((highlight) => (
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <i class={`${highlight.icon} text-2xl text-cyan-500 mr-3`}></i>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">{highlight.title}</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">{highlight.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

        <!-- Student Work Showcase section -->
      <section class="bg-white py-16">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">學生作品展示</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 text-center mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            點擊下方作品直接試玩學生們在 AI 遊戲編程課程中創作的精彩遊戲！從經典的井字棋到創新的自製遊戲，每個作品都展現了學生們的創意和編程技能。
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Wooden Tic-tac-toe Game -->
            <a href="/games/ai-game-coding/WoodenTicTac/index.html" target="_blank" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow cursor-pointer">
              <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 bg-gray-100">
                <Image 
                  src={ticTacToe1} 
                  alt="木製井字棋遊戲作品" 
                  width={400}
                  height={300}
                  class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">木製井字棋遊戲</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">具有木製質感的經典井字棋遊戲，結合傳統與現代設計</p>
              </div>
            </a>

            <!-- Tic-tac-tactics Game -->
            <a href="/games/ai-game-coding/TicTacTactics/index.html" target="_blank" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow cursor-pointer">
              <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 bg-gray-100">
                <Image 
                  src={ticTacToe2} 
                  alt="井字棋戰術遊戲作品" 
                  width={400}
                  height={300}
                  class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">井字棋戰術遊戲</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">加入戰術元素的創新井字棋，考驗策略思維</p>
              </div>
            </a>

            <!-- Sudoku Game -->
            <a href="/games/ai-game-coding/SudokuMaster/index.html" target="_blank" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow cursor-pointer">
              <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 bg-gray-100">
                <Image 
                  src={sudoku} 
                  alt="數獨遊戲作品" 
                  width={400}
                  height={300}
                  class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">數獨大師</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">經典數獨遊戲的完整實現，包含提示功能和難度等級</p>
              </div>
            </a>
            
            <!-- Minesweeper Game -->
            <a href="/games/ai-game-coding/MinefieldChallenge/index.html" target="_blank" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow cursor-pointer">
              <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 bg-gray-100">
                <Image 
                  src={minesweeper} 
                  alt="踩地雷遊戲作品" 
                  width={400}
                  height={300}
                  class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">踩地雷挑戰</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">經典踩地雷遊戲的網頁版本，考驗邏輯思維能力</p>
              </div>
            </a>

            <!-- Pac-Man Game -->
            <a href="/games/ai-game-coding/PacManChase/index.html" target="_blank" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow cursor-pointer">
              <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 bg-gray-100">
                <Image 
                  src={pacman} 
                  alt="食鬼遊戲作品" 
                  width={400}
                  height={300}
                  class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">食鬼追逐遊戲</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">經典食鬼遊戲的重新詮釋，展現動畫和遊戲邏輯的結合</p>
              </div>
            </a>

            <!-- Chinese Puzzle Game -->
            <a href="/games/ai-game-coding/ChinesePuzzle/index.html" target="_blank" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow cursor-pointer">
              <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 bg-gray-100">
                <Image 
                  src={chinesePuzzleDemo} 
                  alt="中國拼圖遊戲作品" 
                  width={400}
                  height={300}
                  class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">中國拼圖遊戲</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">傳統中國益智遊戲的現代化實現，學習成語和中文</p>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>



      <!-- Student Testimonials -->
      <div class="mt-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 to-blue-50 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">學生心得分享</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-quote-left text-2xl text-cyan-500 mr-3"></i>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">AI 編程初體驗</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
              "沒想到編程可以這麼有趣！使用 AI 工具幫助我設計遊戲邏輯，讓我能專注在創意上。完成第一個井字棋遊戲時，那種成就感真的很棒！"
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-quote-left text-2xl text-cyan-500 mr-3"></i>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">從零到一的突破</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
              "作為編程新手，這個課程讓我學會了如何與 AI 協作開發。現在我不僅能製作遊戲，還能將作品分享給朋友們玩，真的很興奮！"
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Course Content Section -->
  <SingleCourseContent 
    items={curriculumItems}
    hours="6-8 小時"
  />

  <QnASection faqs={faqItems} />
  <!-- Related News Section -->
  <RelatedNews courseTags={courseData.tags} courseTitle={courseData.title} />



  <!-- Contact section -->
  <ContactSection subtitle="想了解更多關於人工智能網頁遊戲編程工作坊的資訊？歡迎聯絡我們，我們會為您提供詳細的課程安排和報名資訊。" />
</Layout>


